Package: labelembeddings
Type: Package
Title: MCMC Sampling from the Posterior of a Dirichlet Mulitnomial Model
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Katharina Hechinger
Maintainer: Katharina Hechinger <katharina.hechinger@stat.uni-muenchen.de>
Description: We model annotations using a Dirichlet Multinomial Model, estimated with an empirical bayes approach. For the annotations, embeddings reflecting the annotation uncertainty can be estimated by sampling from the posterior distributions.
